Alaska Department (1867-03-30)

1867/03/30 -> 1884/05/16

The United States acquired Alaska from Russia. Presidential proclamation issued 20 June 1867. Alaska was considered an "unorganized territory" with no organized civil government.

(Parry, 134:331-335; Swindler, 1:163-168)
